Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.82,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\bord0\fs30\fsp0\c&H727476&\an7\3c&HBCB7B2&\frz359.5\pos(634.4,400.667)}小学生及以下免费
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我有没有零钱呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,里头还挺宽敞的
